&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note&lt;/strong&gt; that the output line is to include the  &lt;code&gt;‚Äò-‚Äô&lt;/code&gt; s and spacing exactly as shown in the table above and demonstrated in the Sample Output below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition, after each output line, you must print an empty line.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-input&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-input&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Input&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
