ISAPALINILAPASI&lt;br /&gt;
2A3MEAS&lt;br /&gt;
ATOYOTA&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;sample-output&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#sample-output&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Sample Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NOTAPALINDROME -- is not a palindrome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ISAPALINILAPASI -- is a regular palindrome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2A3MEAS -- is a mirrored string.&lt;/p&gt;
